title: Getting Dicked Down with Trey Lewis
itunes:title: Getting Dicked Down with Trey Lewis
description:
He's used to playing for 25,000 screaming fans, but this week Trey Lewis takes the stage with Bunnie to bare all. The country singer turned viral hitmaker talks about hitting it big in 2020 with his hit "Getting Dicked Down in Dallas", and how the newfound attention changed his life. He also talks with Bunnie about getting sober at a young age, his big tour coming up, and gives a glimpse into his private life.
